ading-[1.7]">That explains everything — Cloudflare's "Under Construction" / Access policy is blocking all crawlers including Google. So it's not an SEO problem yet, it's a visibility gate.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Once you flip it to public, that's when SEO actually starts mattering. So the good news is nothing is broken — you just haven't opened the doors yet.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">When you're ready to go public, the SEO launch checklist will be:</p>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Remove Cloudflare Access restriction</strong></li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Verify in Google Search Console + submit sitemap</strong></li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Check robots.txt exists and isn't blocking anything</strong></li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Fix the two sitemap gaps</strong> (<code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">/exporters/other/</code> and <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">/tools/</code>)</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Audit on-page SEO</strong> — titles, descriptions, H1s, keyword targeting per page</li>
</ol>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">For now the most useful thing I can do is audit your page files directly as you share them — titles, meta descriptions, heading structure, copy quality — so everything is dialled in before you go live. Want to start with the homepage or one of the exporter pages?</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="flex justify-start opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-within:opacity-100 transition" role="group" aria-label="Message actions"><div class="text-text-300"><div class="text-text-300 flex items-stretch justify-between"><button type="button" data-cds="Button" class="cds-reset group/btn relative isolate inline-flex shrink-0 items-center justify-center gap-1.5 whitespace-nowrap select-none border-0 outline-none rounded h-control font-sans text-body font-medium [&amp;:disabled:not([aria-busy])]:opacity-50 disabled:pointer-events-none transition-shadow duration-fast focus-visible:shadow-focus text-primary aria-pressed:text-accent aspect-square w-control px-0  !text-muted hover:!text-primary" aria-label="Copy" data-testid="action-bar-copy"><span aria-hidden="true" class="absolute -z-[1] rounded-[inherit] transition-colors duration-fast group-focus-visible/btn:shadow-[inset_0_0_0_1px_var(--cds-page-bg)] bg-transparent group-hover/btn:bg-fill-ghost-hover group-aria-expanded/btn:bg-fill-ghost-hover inset-0 group-aria-pressed/btn:bg-accent group-hover/btn:group-aria-pressed/btn:bg-accent cds-btn-squish "></span><span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 "><span class="relative"><span data-cds="Icon" class="transition-all opacity-100 scale-100" aria-hidden="true" style="font-family: var(--font-anthropicons, Anthropicons-Variable); font-feature-settings: &quot;liga&quot; 0; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-style: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; line-height: 1; width: 1em; height: 1em; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0; user-select: none;