<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Homepage</strong> (<code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">index.html</code>)</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>One exporter page</strong> (e.g. <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">exporters/claude/index.html</code>)</li>
