<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>favicon.ico</strong> — the tiny icon that appears in browser tabs, bookmarks, and browser history. Usually 16×16 or 32×32 pixels.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>og-image.png</strong> — the preview image that appears when someone shares your link on Twitter/X, LinkedIn, Slack, iMessage, etc. Should be 1200×630 pixels — much bigger, almost like a mini banner ad for your site.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">You don't have one set at all right now, which means shared links just show a blank card with text only. Worth making one — even something simple like your logo centered on your indigo/purple gradient background with "Export AI conversations to PDF" underneath it would look great. Want me to generate the HTML/SVG for one you could screenshot or render?</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="flex justify-start opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-within:opacity-100 transition" role="group" aria-label="Message actions"><div class="text-text-300"><div class="text-text-300 flex items-stretch justify-between"><button type="button" data-cds="Button" class="cds-reset group/btn relative isolate inline-flex shrink-0 items-center justify-center gap-1.5 whitespace-nowrap select-none border-0 outline-none rounded h-control font-sans text-body font-medium [&amp;:disabled:not([aria-busy])]:opacity-50 disabled:pointer-events-none transition-shadow duration-fast focus-visible:shadow-focus text-primary aria-pressed:text-accent aspect-square w-control px-0  !text-muted hover:!text-primary" aria-label="Copy" data-testid="action-bar-copy"><span aria-hidden="true" class="absolute -z-[1] rounded-[inherit] transition-colors duration-fast group-focus-visible/btn:shadow-[inset_0_0_0_1px_var(--cds-page-bg)] bg-transparent group-hover/btn:bg-fill-ghost-hover group-aria-expanded/btn:bg-fill-ghost-hover inset-0 group-aria-pressed/btn:bg-accent group-hover/btn:group-aria-pressed/btn:bg-accent cds-btn-squish "></span><span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 "><span class="relative"><span data-cds="Icon" class="transition-all opacity-100 scale-100" aria-hidden="true" style="font-family: var(--font-anthropicons, Anthropicons-Variable); font-feature-settings: &quot;liga&quot; 0; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-style: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; line-height: 1; width: 1em; height: 1em; disp